Leave management 
coded in C# ASP.NET Core MVC
SQL Database, included in the project Repo in the folder /db
Used repository pattern  to create an abstraction layer between the data access layer and the business logic layer.
To this application, clone https://github.com/gibsjoseph/Leave-management-joseph 
Import the sql db found this directory /db
Edit the connection string depending on your sql server instance  /Context/LeaveMgtContex.cs file
Build the application
Run the application
First the index page displays the leave and create others
You Can navigate the Employee, and Department
